ddf.catalog.filter

Interface ArgumentBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeotoolsFunctionExpressionBuilder

    public interface ArgumentBuilder
    This code is experimental. While this interface is functional and tested, it may change or be removed in a future version of the library. Completes the fluent API to create a Filter for a function that takes N parameters.
